Package: injuryExplorer
Title: ER Injury Data Explorer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Funmi", "Olawole", 
           email = "aolaw002@ucr.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for exploring emergency room injury data
    from the Mastering Shiny ER injuries case study. The app provides
    graphical summaries, numerical summaries, and patient narratives
    based on injury characteristics.
